flowchart TD
    REQ([Incoming HTTP Request]) --> PANIC[1. Panic Recovery<br/>defer recover]
    PANIC --> HEALTHZ{2. Path == /healthz?}
    HEALTHZ -->|Yes| PASS[Pass through to handler<br/>Skip remaining middleware]
    HEALTHZ -->|No| AUTH{3. Bearer token or<br/>OAuth token valid?}
    AUTH -->|No| R401[401 unauthorized]
    AUTH -->|Yes| APIKEY[4. X-Gemini-API-Key extraction<br/>store in request context]
    APIKEY --> RATE{5. Rate limit<br/>token bucket allows?}
    RATE -->|No| R429[429 rate_limited<br/>+ Retry-After header]
    RATE -->|Yes| SEM{6. Concurrency semaphore<br/>slot available within 5s?}
    SEM -->|No| R503[503 server_busy]
    SEM -->|Yes| BODY[7. Body size limit<br/>MaxBytesReader 15MB]
    BODY --> BODYOK{Body read OK?}
    BODYOK -->|Size exceeded| R413[413 request_too_large]
    BODYOK -->|Other error| R400[400 bad_request]
    BODYOK -->|OK| HANDLER[MCP Handler<br/>Tool execution]
    HANDLER --> RESP([Response to client])

    style R401 fill:#fcc,stroke:#c33
    style R429 fill:#fcc,stroke:#c33
    style R503 fill:#fcc,stroke:#c33
    style R413 fill:#fcc,stroke:#c33
    style R400 fill:#fcc,stroke:#c33
